language Essence 1.3

letting n be 4
letting max_time be 5

letting Task be domain record {
    duration:    int(1..5),
    start:       int(0..max_time),
    finish:      int(1..max_time)
}

letting prd be [(0, 0), (1, 2), (1, 1), (2, 0)]

find tasks: matrix indexed by [int(1..n)] of Task

such that
    $ finish = start + duration
    forAll i: int(1..n) .
        tasks[i][finish] = tasks[i][start] + tasks[i][duration],

    $ Precedence with lag
    forAll i: int(1..n) .
        ((prd[i][1] > 0) ->
            (tasks[i][start] >= tasks[prd[i][1]][finish] + prd[i][2])),

    $ Symmetry breaking
    tasks[1][start] = 0
